<hr id="read-marker">

United Left Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: [+ uspd_colour +];">**USPD**</span> + <span style="color: [+ kpd_colour +];">**KPD**</span>[? if sapd_formed:+ <span style="color: #9B0000;">**SAPD**</span>?]): [+ left_coalition_wurttemberg +]% 

Weimar Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?]<span style="color: #000000;"> + **Z**</span>): [+ weimar_coalition_wurttemberg +]% 

Grand Coalition (<span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>?][? if csvd_r_wurttemberg > 0: + <span style="color: #8A50E4;">**CSVD**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?]<span style="color: #000000;"> + **Z**</span>): [+ grand_coalition_wurttemberg +]%

Bourgeois Coalition (<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: [+ dvp_colour +];">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?] [? if kvp_formed :+ <span style="color: #0087DC;">**KVP**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #006400;">**WbWB**</span>): [+ true_bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg +]%

Right-Wing Coalition (<span style="color: [+ dnvp_colour +];">**DNVP**</span> + <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**NSDAP**</span>): [+ right_coalition_wurttemberg +]%

@wurttemberg_coalition_menu

- @spd_majority_wurttemberg
- @weimar_coalition_wurttemberg
- @grand_coalition_wurttemberg
- @bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg
- @bourgeois_right_coalition_wurttemberg
- @left_coalition_wurttemberg
- @social_catholic_coalition_wurttemberg
- @no_coalition_wurttemberg

@spd_majority_wurttemberg
title: SPD majority
subtitle: We can govern alone
view-if: spd_r_wurttemberg >= 50
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; catholic_spd += 1; catholic_z -= 2; rural_spd += 1; rural_others -= 2; wurttemberg_gov = "SPD"

@weimar_coalition_wurttemberg
title: A Weimar Coalition will be formed
choose-if: weimar_coalition_wurttemberg >= 50 and z_relation >= 80
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 1; ddp_relation += 1; wurttemberg_gov = "Weimar"

@grand_coalition_wurttemberg
title: A Grand Coalition will be formed
choose-if: grand_coalition_wurttemberg >= 50 and ddp_relation >= 25 and dvp_relation >= 60 and z_relation >= 75
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 2; dvp_relation += 3; wurttemberg_gov = "Grand"

@bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg
title: Another Bourgeois Coalition
choose-if: true_bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg >= 60
view-if: right_bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg < 50
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; wurttemberg_gov = "Bourgeois"

@bourgeois_right_coalition_wurttemberg
title: Another Bourgeois Coalition
view-if: z_relation < 80 and dvp_relation <= 50
choose-if: right_bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg >= 50
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; wurttemberg_gov = "Right"

@left_coalition_wurttemberg
title: A Coalition of the Left will be formed
subtitle: We will work alongside the KPD
choose-if: left_coalition_wurttemberg >= 50 and kpd_relation >= 65
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; ruarl_kpd += 3; rural_others -= 2; catholic_dvp -= 1; catholic_spd += 1; wurttemberg_gov = "Left"

@right_wing_coalition_wurttemberg
title: The right forms a government...
subtitle: This doesn't make sense.
choose-if: right_coalition_wurttemberg >= 50
view-if: right_coalition_wurttemberg >= 50
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; rural_nsdap += 2; catholic_nsdap += 2; wurttemberg_gov = "Right"

This can't end well...

@social_catholic_coalition_wurttemberg
title: Why not form a <span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**Social**</span>-<span style="color: [+ z_colour +];">**Catholic**</span> Coalition?
view-if: (z_r_wurttemberg + spd_r_wurttemberg) >= 50 and z_relation >= 90 and ddp_r_wurttemberg <= 5.5
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 2; ddp_relation -= 2; wurttemberg_gov = "Social-Catholic"

The poor performance of the <span style="color: [+ ddp_colour +];">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> has allowed us to try a <span style="color: [+ spd_colour +];">**Social**</span>-<span style="color: [+ z_colour +];">**Catholic**</span> Coalition.
  
@no_coalition_wurttemberg
title: There is no possible government arrangement
subtitle: New elections will be called...
on-arrival: wurttemberg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 3; rural_dnvp += 2
view-if: bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg < 50 and weimar_coalition_wurttemberg < 50 and z_relation < 80
